    DESCRIPTION = One use only. At the beginning of any phase (friend or foe's) announce you are using Skalm. The bearer is instantly cured of any wounds suffered so far. Skalm is of no use to models that are already dead. Skalm can only be used by the bearer, sharing such a precious thing is not something a Skaven would contemplate.
    ALLOWED_UNITS = Warlord, Grey Seer, Assassin, Warlock Engineer, Chieftain, Plague Priest
    RESTRICTIONS = Limit - 1

