    DESCRIPTION = One use only. A character equipped with such a weapon can throw it in any Shooting phase. The Death Globe is thrown just as the Brass Orb. All models touched by the template suffer a wound on the result of a 4+, with no armour save allowed.
    ALLOWED_UNITS = Warlock Engineer
